# File Structure

```
cursor/
├── index.html          # Single HTML page — all markup lives here
├── style.css           # All styles — no CSS modules, no preprocessors
├── script.js           # All client-side JS — no bundler
├── README.md
├── .gitignore
└── .cursor/
    ├── hooks.json          # Cursor lifecycle hooks config
    ├── hooks/
    │   ├── before-shell.sh # Blocks dangerous shell commands
    │   ├── on-edit.sh      # Logs AI file edits to .cursor/logs/edits.log
    │   └── on-stop.sh      # Logs sessions + macOS notification
    ├── logs/               # Auto-generated; gitignored
    │   ├── edits.log
    │   └── sessions.log
    ├── commands/
    │   ├── php-server.md   # Slash command: start PHP dev server
    │   └── open-browser.md # Slash command: open site in browser
    └── rules/              # Cursor AI rules (this folder)
```

## Conventions

- All source files are at the project root — no `src/` subdirectory
- There is exactly one HTML file (`index.html`); do not add more pages
- Do not introduce a build step, bundler, or package manager
